# sampling/flow_match_smoke.mojo — GPU smoke + parity driver for the Z-Image
# flow-matching scheduler (sampling/flow_match.mojo).
#
# Compares against the numpy oracle (sampling/parity/gen_flow_match_reference.py,
# seed=2468) via ParityHarness. THIS FILE IS GENERATED by that same parity dir's
# emit step — do not hand-edit the inlined reference arrays. Gate: schedule
# arrays match to ~1e-5 (cos ~1.0, max_abs <= 1e-5); one update step cos >= 0.999.
#
# Run: pixi run mojo run -I . serenitymojo/sampling/flow_match_smoke.mojo

